{"tha-ap486:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap486:0.2":"Pamsukulavagga ","tha-ap486:0.3":"4 Nanathavikattheraapadana ","tha-ap486:1.1":"“Dakkhine himavantassa, ","tha-ap486:1.2":"sukato assamo mama; ","tha-ap486:1.3":"Uttamattham gavesanto, ","tha-ap486:1.4":"vasami vipine tada. ","tha-ap486:2.1":"Labhalabhena santuttho, ","tha-ap486:2.2":"mulena ca phalena ca; ","tha-ap486:2.3":"Anvesanto acariyam, ","tha-ap486:2.4":"vasami ekako aham. ","tha-ap486:3.1":"Sumedho nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap486:3.2":"loke uppajji tavade; ","tha-ap486:3.3":"Catusaccam pakaseti, ","tha-ap486:3.4":"uddharanto mahajanam. ","tha-ap486:4.1":"Naham sunomi sambuddham, ","tha-ap486:4.2":"napi me koci samsati; ","tha-ap486:4.3":"Atthavasse atikkante, ","tha-ap486:4.4":"assosim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap486:5.1":"Aggidarum niharitva, ","tha-ap486:5.2":"sammajjitvana assamam; ","tha-ap486:5.3":"Kharibharam gahetvana, ","tha-ap486:5.4":"nikkhamim vipina aham. ","tha-ap486:6.1":"Ekarattim vasantoham, ","tha-ap486:6.2":"gamesu nigamesu ca; ","tha-ap486:6.3":"Anupubbena candavatim, ","tha-ap486:6.4":"tadaham upasankamim. ","tha-ap486:7.1":"Bhagava tamhi samaye, ","tha-ap486:7.2":"sumedho lokanayako; ","tha-ap486:7.3":"Uddharanto bahu satte, ","tha-ap486:7.4":"deseti amatam padam. ","tha-ap486:8.1":"Janakayamatikkamma, ","tha-ap486:8.2":"vanditva jinasagaram; ","tha-ap486:8.3":"Ekamsam ajinam katva, ","tha-ap486:8.4":"santhavim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap486:9.1":"‘Tuvam sattha ca ketu ca, ","tha-ap486:9.2":"dhajo yupo ca paninam; ","tha-ap486:9.3":"Parayano patittha ca, ","tha-ap486:9.4":"dipo ca dvipaduttamo. ","tha-ap486:10.1":"Ekavisatimam bhanavaram. ","tha-ap486:11.1":"Nepunno dassane viro, ","tha-ap486:11.2":"taresi janatam tuvam; ","tha-ap486:11.3":"Natthanno tarako loke, ","tha-ap486:11.4":"tavuttaritaro mune. ","tha-ap486:12.1":"Sakka theve kusaggena, ","tha-ap486:12.2":"pametum sagaruttame; ","tha-ap486:12.3":"Na tveva tava sabbannu, ","tha-ap486:12.4":"nanam sakka pametave. ","tha-ap486:13.1":"Tuladande thapetvana, ","tha-ap486:13.2":"mahim sakka dharetave; ","tha-ap486:13.3":"Na tveva tava pannaya, ","tha-ap486:13.4":"pamanamatthi cakkhuma. ","tha-ap486:14.1":"Akaso minitum sakka, ","tha-ap486:14.2":"rajjuya angulena va; ","tha-ap486:14.3":"Na tveva tava sabbannu, ","tha-ap486:14.4":"silam sakka pametave. ","tha-ap486:15.1":"Mahasamudde udakam, ","tha-ap486:15.2":"akaso ca vasundhara; ","tha-ap486:15.3":"Parimeyyani etani, ","tha-ap486:15.4":"appameyyosi cakkhuma’. ","tha-ap486:16.1":"Chahi gathahi sabbannum, ","tha-ap486:16.2":"kittayitva mahayasam; ","tha-ap486:16.3":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap486:16.4":"tunhi atthasaham tada. ","tha-ap486:17.1":"Yam vadanti sumedhoti, ","tha-ap486:17.2":"bhuripannam sumedhasam; ","tha-ap486:17.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap486:17.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap486:18.1":"‘Yo me nanam pakittesi, ","tha-ap486:18.2":"vippasannena cetasa; ","tha-ap486:18.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap486:18.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap486:19.1":"Sattasattati kappani, ","tha-ap486:19.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap486:19.3":"Sahassakkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap486:19.4":"devarajjam karissati. ","tha-ap486:20.1":"Anekasatakkhattunca, ","tha-ap486:20.2":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap486:20.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap486:20.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap486:21.1":"Devabhuto manusso va, ","tha-ap486:21.2":"punnakammasamahito; ","tha-ap486:21.3":"Anunamanasankappo, ","tha-ap486:21.4":"tikkhapanno bhavissati’. ","tha-ap486:22.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap486:22.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap486:22.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap486:22.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap486:23.1":"Agara abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap486:23.2":"pabbajissatikincano; ","tha-ap486:23.3":"Jatiya sattavassena, ","tha-ap486:23.4":"arahattam phusissati. ","tha-ap486:24.1":"Yato sarami attanam, ","tha-ap486:24.2":"yato pattosmi sasanam; ","tha-ap486:24.3":"Etthantare na janami, ","tha-ap486:24.4":"cetanam amanoramam. ","tha-ap486:25.1":"Samsaritva bhave sabbe, ","tha-ap486:25.2":"sampattanubhavim aham; ","tha-ap486:25.3":"Bhoge me unata natthi, ","tha-ap486:25.4":"phalam nanassa thomane. ","tha-ap486:26.1":"Tiyaggi nibbuta mayham, ","tha-ap486:26.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap486:26.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","tha-ap486:26.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","tha-ap486:27.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap486:27.2":"yam nanamathavim aham; ","tha-ap486:27.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap486:27.4":"phalam nanassa thomane. ","tha-ap486:28.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap486:28.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap486:28.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap486:29.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap486:29.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap486:29.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap486:30.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap486:30.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap486:30.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap486:31.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma nanathaviko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap486:32.1":"Nanathavikattherassapadanam catuttham. "}